  "text": "Specimens are 2D laminated twill woven. The PyroSic® composite (SiRC) is a silicon-carbide-fiber-reinforced glass ceramic composite, with a 42% fiber volumetric ratio and 12% porosity. It has been developed for thermostructural applications at temperature up to 1000˚C [CITATION_1] .",
