    "138256549": {
      "title": "User-Friendly Composites That Take the Heat",
      "abstract": "For high-temperature composites, finding a good balance between performance, convenience and cost is a recurring challenge. With a new generation of glass-ceramic matrix composites processed like CFRP and designed for temperatures up to 1000°C, Pyromeral Systems is opening new opportunities for composites in high-temperature applications."
